@SafeVault_HostAddress = http://localhost:5194
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### 회원가입
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Test@1234",
    "confirmPassword": "Test@1234"
}

###

### 로그인
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "Admin@123!"
}

###

### 현재 사용자 정보 (인증 필요)
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 토큰 검증 (인증 필요)
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/auth/validate
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ===== 관리자 API (Admin 역할 필요) =====

### 대시보드 통계
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/dashboard
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 사용자 목록 조회
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 특정 사용자 조회
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 사용자 역할 변경
PUT {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/2/role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "userId": 2,
    "newRole": "Admin"
}

###

### 사용자 비활성화
PUT {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/2/deactivate
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 사용자 활성화
PUT {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/users/2/activate
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 검증 로그 조회
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/logs?page=1&pageSize=50
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 차단된 로그만 조회
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/logs?page=1&pageSize=50&filter=BLOCKED
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 차단 패턴 목록 조회
GET {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/patterns
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 차단 패턴 추가
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/patterns
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "pattern": "<marquee",
    "patternType": 1,
    "description": "marquee 태그 차단"
}

###

### 차단 패턴 토글 (활성화/비활성화)
PUT {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/admin/patterns/1/toggle
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ===== 폼 API =====

### 입력값 검증
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/form/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "testuser123",
    "fieldType": "USERNAME"
}

###

### SQL 인젝션 테스트 (차단되어야 함)
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/form/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "' OR '1'='1",
    "fieldType": "USERNAME"
}

###

### XSS 테스트 (차단되어야 함)
POST {{SafeVault_HostAddress}}/api/form/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "value": "<script>alert('xss')</script>",
    "fieldType": "USERNAME"
}

###
